description:
&lt;p&gt;St Richard&#39;s Hospital in Chichester has an opportunity to employ 2 full time ward clerks in temporary positions to support winter pressures and the opening of 2 new areas. This would be an ideal chance for someone interested in working at the hospital to experience this role and provide them with a stepping stone into a possible permanent position in the future.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role is a busy and varied one, and the successful applicant would gain valuable skills and knowledge of the processes within the hospital, as well as being an integral part of the ward team, led by the Ward Sister. You will have daily patient and relative contact and provide a vital link in communications with them, as well as the multidisciplinary team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We look forward to meeting you and welcoming you to the teams!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Namejackie dominickJob titlematronEmail addressjackie.dominick@nhs.netTelephone number01243 788122 ext 35228&lt;/p&gt;
